@host = http://localhost:5080

### Health check
GET {{host}}/

### List all tasks  (no filtering yet — the CHAOS demo adds ?status= / ?priority=)
GET {{host}}/tasks

### Get one task (paste an id from the list above)
GET {{host}}/tasks/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Create a task
POST {{host}}/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Try the Task Tracker API",
  "status": "Open",
  "priority": "High"
}

### Update a task
PUT {{host}}/tasks/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Try the Task Tracker API (updated)",
  "status": "InProgress",
  "priority": "Medium"
}

### Delete a task
DELETE {{host}}/tasks/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
